<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../static/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../static/css/home.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="../static/Images/icons/lol-league-of-Legends-logo.png">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Sans+Pro:ital,wght@0,200;0,400;0,700;1,200;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>League of Legends - Home Page</title>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('header') %>
        <main>
            <section>
                <img src="https://preview.redd.it/in73r6sbixz31.png?width=4096&format=png&auto=webp&s=810fa4aef8f17b2ccf3ca4c18601eb731904d37e" alt="Main_picture_bg" id="img_home_s1">
            </section>
            <section class="bg_blue1 white">
                <div class="title1 wrapped bold">
                    What you can find
                </div>
                <article class="displayFlex article_bubble padding_section">
                    <div class="bubble_info">
                        <h1>Events</h1>
                        <p>End of worlds</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bubble_info">
                        <h1>Change of ADC</h1>
                        <p>All teams have choose their teamnates. </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bubble_info">
                        <h1>New caracter</h1>
                        <p>In december 2021</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </section>
            <section class="bg_blue2 white">
                <div class="title2 wrapped bold">
                    game characters
                </div>
                <section class="displayFlex align_item padding_section">
                    <div id="text_GC">
                        <p class="text_imp">
                            Un nombre <strong>colossal de personnages</strong> disponible dès maintenant, alors rejoignez nous pour faire partie des Légendes !
                        </p>
                        <div id="div_playnow">
                            <a href="https://signup.euw.leagueoflegends.com/fr/signup/index" id="button_play" class="dec_none">
                            PLAY NOW
                        </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text_align_center">
                        <img src="https://archive.esportsobserver.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/maxresdefault.jpg" alt="game_caract" id="img_game_caract">
                    </div>
                </section>
            </section>
            <section class="bg_blue3 white">
                <div class="title3 wrapped bold">
                    Teams
                </div>
                <section class="text_align_center padding_section">
                    <div>
                        <p>In this video game, you don't play alone but in teams of five players. Within the team, everyone plays a role in order to achieve victory. There are healers, attackers, ranged characters and many others. So don't hesitate to join
                            us.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <iframe width="75%" height="500" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KbNL9ZyB49c">
                </iframe>
                </section>

            </section>
        </main>

        <%- include('footer') %>
            <!-- Le trait d'union est pour dire à EJS de rendre le HTML brut. -->

</body>

</html>